plyTime":"2017-04-24T04:37:10.000Z","msg":"柒出國際"},{"pid":"3e8e21c83637ed4dfac183a1489d7a2cfcfdef00","tid":214794,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:41:46.000Z","msg":"嘩 小心d呀<br />\n一陣d臭雞港女又報警<br />\n巧京京牙"},{"pid":"f0a7514a55686fa65ff572241520c1e8b1a9f4b6","tid":214794,"uid":57914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:42:20.000Z","msg":"正宗本地雞卵，free range chicks"},{"pid":"f2972b1eeec91cf1e292dbc5939bdc95c96b2645","tid":214794,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:46:29.000Z","msg":"真係可以拎個西黎當8達通用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37103cf1cd0b39c6a7addbf4b14a4db987dde606","tid":214794,"uid":20967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:46:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘩 小心d呀<br />\n一陣d臭雞港女又報警<br />\n巧京京牙</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一陣又post翻你班男人相呀"},{"pid":"a7e3fc3909b2867374b36babfcd9c637e3b1a72d","tid":214794,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:52:26.000Z","msg":"另類做雞法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf89d9c44bb1269492846dd071b7c12a8b2afab","tid":214794,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:53:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嘩 小心d呀<br />\n一陣d臭雞港女又報警<br />\n巧京京牙</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一陣又post翻你班男人相呀</blockquote><br />\n唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嚇屎我啦"},{"pid":"ed3107c181c837aeaedab9924f01e00506dd81cc","tid":214794,"uid":9544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:54:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gn8P54T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna